Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓小葵看到富士山這個計劃完美成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額 我覺得是成功了 大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們以三增卡的山頂為目標繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離山頂還有一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.63,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(524,416)}下山之後的樂趣!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是屏風巖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增卡也是攀爬的名地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵要不要試試看？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前大家一起練習過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這跟攀巖完全不同啊 我還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過了屏風巖就是山頂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後衝刺了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉眼大片美好的景色就展現在我們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前進 前進 前進 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點 再前進一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 已經看得到山頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到…到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠自己的雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼充實的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼空氣這麼清新呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是… 這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 楓 心夏 好漂亮 景色好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 我還是第一次見到小葵這麼能鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我笑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就叫做開心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你的手停住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好吃飯補充能量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重要的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去也要走很多路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 要多吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快樂的時間結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有開始就會有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登上山就還要下山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想擁有更多這樣的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山的時候要讓它稍微長一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握的方式也變了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快下山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山下面有溫泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來的時候有招牌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是真的 在車站附近有溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去的時候泡上一會也是登山的樂趣之一呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉 溫泉 溫泉 溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉 要大家一起泡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不進去泡溫泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是露天的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中學修學旅行時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大家睡著的時候才偷偷進去泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山會容易控制不了速度 很可怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是想溫泉的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得集中精神下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓 下山該怎麼走才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山的話 比起體力還是更靠經驗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順著地勢 順勢下山更好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像這樣 順勢而下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果只能小心地走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為下山容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是來的時候很可怕的路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因為走過一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不覺得可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為什麼呢 感覺好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有長凳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在長凳上休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…膝蓋好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且相當疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 你的膝蓋還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很疼 腳承受了很大的負擔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點哦 在這種平坦的地方是會受傷的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走過了艱險的地方 放心的一瞬間是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我要好好集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膝蓋好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啊 我在膝蓋上綁了護具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便宜的就行 買一個會輕鬆很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕鬆 輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山之前就告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還得走多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 快點到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山的時候沒注意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個現在都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 熊先生 有緣再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 馬上就到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走過登山道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要走很長的路才能到車站呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來的時候還說柏油路好走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到回去的時候竟然這麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渾身是汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摔倒全身都是泥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上感覺糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉 溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,50)}害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定不錯呢 我想快點進去泡溫泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是溫泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳疼 疼 疼 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉 溫泉 溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡澡不可以裹著毛巾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在進浴池之前得要洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉 溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來 果然還是害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓 你的胸部很大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部大也沒有好事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨礙運動 看起來就胖 還重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵也過來這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裏就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是害羞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才不喜歡和大家一起泡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天走了很多路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 2號線出發的假日快速富士山號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途徑大宮 前往小山方向 現在發車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有座位真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣去新秋津 換乘西武池袋線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要2個小時左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是非常的開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想擁有更多這樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 富士山 下次再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未完待續
